'''N-One Medcenter''' was a [[Medcenter/Legends|medcenter]] located in [[Sector N-One/Legends|Sector N-One]] on the original [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|Death Star]]. It contained an Operating Theater and at least one Surgical Suite. Notable personnel assigned to this medcenter included [[Kornell Divini]], [[Zam Stenza]], [[Abu Banu]], and [[Roa (doctor)|Roa]].

It was destroyed along with the rest of the Death Star during the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]] in [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]].

